---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Cyber Security Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional cybersecurity services in the UAE including penetration testing, security audits, compliance consulting, and managed security solutions for businesses."
  path="/services/cyber-security/"
  image="/img/og-cyber.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="cyber-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Cyber Security Services</h2>
      <p>
        In an era of increasing digital threats, protecting your business assets and customer data is paramount. 
        GeneralSoft offers comprehensive cybersecurity services to help organizations in the UAE identify 
        vulnerabilities, strengthen their security posture, and maintain compliance with regulatory requirements.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our team of certified security professionals brings extensive experience across multiple domains — 
        from network security and application security to cloud security and governance. We take a proactive 
        approach to security, identifying and mitigating risks before they can be exploited.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Security Services</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Penetration Testing</h4>
          <p>Comprehensive security testing of your applications, networks, and infrastructure to identify vulnerabilities before attackers do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Security Audits</h4>
          <p>Thorough assessment of your security policies, procedures, and technical controls against industry standards and best practices.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Compliance Consulting</h4>
          <p>Guidance on meeting regulatory requirements including UAE data protection laws, ISO 27001, PCI DSS, and GDPR compliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Managed Security</h4>
          <p>Ongoing security monitoring, incident response, and security operations support to keep your business protected 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Why Security Matters</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Protect sensitive business and customer data from breaches</li>
        <li>Maintain business continuity and avoid costly downtime</li>
        <li>Build trust with customers and partners through strong security practices</li>
        <li>Meet regulatory and compliance requirements in the UAE</li>
        <li>Reduce the financial impact of potential security incidents</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Security Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our security experience spans identity integration, compliance-driven
          architecture, and secure system design for regulated industries.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Azure AD & ADFS Integration — Tier 1 CSP Initiative</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2016 – Mar 2016</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Tech Lead</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Implemented Azure AD and ADFS integration via AD Connect for a
            Microsoft CSP Initiative serving Tier 1 Partners. Designed secure
            subscription-to-VM provisioning with zero-touch, continuous
            deployment scripting. Integrated Azure AD with on-premises Active
            Directory for seamless single sign-on and identity management.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure AD</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">ADFS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">AD Connect</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PowerShell</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">CI/CD</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>HIPAA-Compliant Healthcare Exchange</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2013 – Dec 2013</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Designed and implemented a Healthcare Exchange with full HIPAA
            compliance for EDI X12 transactions (837, 835, 834, 270). Implemented
            secure document routing on Azure with encryption for protected health
            information (PHI). Created secure EDI Viewers for HTML5 and Windows
            Phone with role-based access controls.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">HIPAA</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">EDI X12</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Dynamics CRM</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>PeopleSoft Integration with Azure AD & ADFS</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Aug 2014 – Aug 2014</span>
            <span class="role">PM / Architect / Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Integrated PeopleSoft HR v.8.52 with Exchange 2010 and Azure AD.
            Built a proof-of-concept for extending Active Directory schema for
            Microsoft Exchange 2010 integration with PeopleSoft. Implemented
            Azure AD federation with on-premises ADFS for secure single sign-on
            across cloud and on-premises systems.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure AD</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">ADFS</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PeopleSoft</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Exchange</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">MQSeries</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>SAP Integration with OAuth/Azure SSO</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Feb 2015 – Dec 2015</span>
            <span class="role">Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Refactored SAP meta-data to latest SAP EHP 7 with single sign-on
            using Azure/OAuth. Implemented secure zero-touch deployment with
            continuous integration using TFS and Octopus Deploy. The solution
            ensured secure authentication and authorization across SAP and
            Azure-integrated enterprise systems.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">SAP EHP 7</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">OAuth</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure SSO</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Octopus Deploy</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Compliance Frameworks</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>PCI DSS v4:</strong> Payment card industry data security standards</li>
        <li><strong>SOC 2:</strong> Service organization control reports for data security</li>
        <li><strong>HIPAA:</strong> Healthcare data privacy and security requirements</li>
        <li><strong>SOX:</strong> Sarbanes-Oxley ITGC compliance</li>
        <li><strong>UAE Regulations:</strong> Local data protection and cybersecurity frameworks</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our cybersecurity services.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>How often should we perform security testing?</summary>
            <p>We recommend penetration testing at least annually, or whenever significant changes are made to your infrastructure or applications. Continuous monitoring is ideal for critical systems.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Do you help with UAE data protection compliance?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We provide consulting services to help your organization comply with UAE data protection regulations, including the UAE Data Protection Law and sector-specific requirements.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>What is included in a security audit?</summary>
            <p>A security audit includes review of your security policies, network architecture assessment, application security testing, access control review, and recommendations for improvement.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Secure Your Business Today</h2>
        <p>Contact our cybersecurity team to schedule a security assessment or discuss your protection needs.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
